# BUG FIX WORKFLOW (Compact)

Use this compact checklist to avoid context bloat. For full details, see @Rules/Workflows/bug-fix-workflow.md.

## PHASES
- TRIAGE → DIAGNOSIS → IMPLEMENTATION → TESTING → COMPLETE

## LOAD MINIMALLY
- Error location ±30 lines
- Direct method dependencies
- Interface/contract of the component
- Related test file if it exists

## SECURITY FIRST
- Validate input, check authorization, CSRF/XSS/SQLi scan

## FIX TEMPLATE
```csharp
// BUG: #{id} - {desc}
// ROOT CAUSE: {issue}
// FIX: {approach}
// VERIFIED: {how}
```

## VERIFY
- dotnet build
- dotnet test --filter "FullyQualifiedName~{TestClass}"
- Minimal manual checks; avoid loading entire solution context

